{"tid":252811,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人可以陪我傾下計","createTime":"2017-05-22T00:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T12:38:35.000Z","uid":5136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41dc112d401c09746ffffccb2d0fb5cc6c631130","tid":252811,"uid":5136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T00:54:54.000Z","msg":"早幾個禮拜同女朋友散左<br />\n咁佢就係個比較細個同幼稚小小既人 但佢有時都幾做到女朋友既本分 會送野 煮野食 有時候睇落去會覺得sweet<br />\n咁我就係一種比較唔識表達 但係心入面對佢都好重視 都會煮野食 送佢翻工咁(大家都係大學生做兼職<br />\n原本一開始都無咩事 但佢既性格就愈黎愈浮上面<br />\n佢有時候會覺得我好唔識關心佢 或者我要佢改過一啲缺點時佢會起曬鋼<br />\n但係啲缺點我覺得佢改左會好好多 不過佢就話咁樣好唔自然<br />\n之後因爲呢兩種價值觀大家吵左好耐 最後散埋<br />\n其實自己真係好鐘意佢<br />\n諗緊追唔追翻佢 又驚佢會覺得我咁熱情係理所當然 但係佢就話唔想再忍我咁樣<br />\n好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4675533bc5725da25c7d384173cc0210dd5053cf","tid":252811,"uid":32298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T01:07:38.000Z","msg":"幫樓主推下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">btw未拍過拖，都無咩意見畀你</span>"},{"pid":"7714b8c62b17f604f9639dcb7db111730496a7c8","tid":252811,"uid":5136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T01:36:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫樓主推下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">btw未拍過拖，都無咩意見畀你</span></blockquote><br />\n有勞有勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18923e380f4f235111dc40b53835e3149e7d3e3","tid":252811,"uid":5136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"朝早無人上感情台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f527040a23d6889ac4749428c9049ce5942ae049","tid":252811,"uid":113661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T03:39:17.000Z","msg":"叔叔比個愛的抱抱你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b7e26091e1b11e0de7239daed136bc011becff","tid":252811,"uid":61264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep