hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f5e90cf784e4d75e7f7a30c66e5a77dc2cfb48","tid":252811,"uid":5136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T06:40:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係個唔識表達自己既人<br />\n到而家都唔知條女嬲左我d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女仔都係想人氹姐 加油去馬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff00e3969a5f977cd8e8e9debc28ecf31f1d7abc","tid":252811,"uid":118011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T06:44:32.000Z","msg":"有咩缺點咁巴閉要人改啊"},{"pid":"9f362fd34080948dc1b913228e9eb8efc969241e","tid":252811,"uid":5136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T12:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩缺點咁巴閉要人改啊</blockquote><br />\n例如係對父母要有返少少禮貌 我只係就咁講左一句<br />\n 咁佢就起晒鋼 話呀媽黎既所以要用最自然既態度去對待都可以 <br />\n之後就話我唔企佢果邊 強行將佢改變"}]}